Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:11.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:15.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:17.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:36.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:43.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:48.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:53.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:59.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:04.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:11.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:14.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:18.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:27.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:32.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:11.10,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}爱因爱而愈加沉重 却拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:15.58,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在爱变为恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:17.68,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.73,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永远是这眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:25.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}仿佛被吞噬之物的写实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.86,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在这被扭曲的进退两难之时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.82,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:36.17,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也渐行着冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:43.60,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毁灭与理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.45,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:48.98,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这难道是灭亡之尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:53.37,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否认这一切 挺身面对之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:59.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即将殒落之时 都不会逃离眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:04.44,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，无论如何也要找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:11.12,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的双眸 双手的温存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:14.63,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}说什么「爱总是只给我带来伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:18.30,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低声细语 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.30,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐惧中哭泣么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.45,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}认识着软弱 渴望着坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:27.26,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当不再恐惧而满怀信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:32.06,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那将是真实的爱
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:18.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:33.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:40.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:48.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:57.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:04.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:11.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:21.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:18.49,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当纯真变为单纯的力量 世界由此诞生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:33.03,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透过玻璃橱 感触着这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:40.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}举起的手无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:48.80,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}却如同坠落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:57.12,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:04.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:11.94,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:21.11,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能把想做的事情告诉我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要洋装
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃很多吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸妈妈见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强大了 更本没有打得必要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是变革者的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按捺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭!? 首都全域!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和苏伊尔国王会谈的同志们也被卷进去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马哈尔支部长他…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦使用核武器了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是空中的大功率激光攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento-Mori 取得了预想之上的战果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这个力量的话 就能轻松灭掉反政府势力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现实的角度 消灭了世界上的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a}拉格朗日3 资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser到达TRANS-AM极限时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我看到了大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越理论极限的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 TWIN-DRIVE远远超乎我们的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是不得了的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 你身体情况的数据我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今怎么能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正保守一点多尽一份力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐 观测系统探查到地球圈内有异常热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻到舰桥来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…卫星兵器…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能借用了太阳光发电系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然得到的情报还很少…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哪里开的火?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东 苏伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 里本斯·阿尔马克的做法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修补完成后 托勒密出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开联邦卫星兵器的破坏任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到各自的岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 有些话要对大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一群人背地里操纵联邦 妄图支配世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的名字是「变革者」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用太阳光发电 从卫星轨道上进行的激光攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的攻击范围…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的宇宙部队已经开始破坏卫星兵器的行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成两个舰队同时攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗舰23艘 MS 43架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是宇宙部队的全部战力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卫星兵器周边A-LAWS正张网以待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这个战力能不能行还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田 天行者方面的联络呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止还没有联系上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON不得不孤军奋战了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由维塔孕育的生物终端 变革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙操纵着A-LAWS 并且掌握着维塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 在我们开始武力介入的5年前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始活动了 是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崔尼蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让3架Gundam Throne参加武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有将搭载拟GN DRIVE的30架GN-X提供给联合国 都是他们干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说他们改变了伊奥利亚的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样 洛克昂和克丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么重大的事情到现在才告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们号称在执行伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是事实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方才很有可能是异端…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS制造的反政府势力的虐杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种做法怎么可能会得到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒A-LAWS 驱逐变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我自身的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 我和他们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致的情况我们都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在最要紧的是破坏敌方卫星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们能做的 只有祈祷宇宙舰队作战成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在阿扎帝斯坦的时候没任何变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐打算舍弃天行者 加入变革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的思考方式是不会迎来真正的变革的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你并非如自己所想那般特别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和杀死哥哥们的家伙联手的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离拉格朗日3的小行星区域还有3266
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要如何去找他们的基地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务请交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒维准尉 身体如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张照片…是您的夫人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 直到2个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入了KATARON的反联邦恐怖行动 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadessa　Garazzo出动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛奈金大佐想出了个有趣的作战方案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人类 已经很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和提艾利亚的机体好像也有新装备追加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是琳达的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待战果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser也能出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到Ptolemaeus的搬运过程 以及和00 TRANS-AM的配合实验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要进行调整作业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要分别了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些话想和你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我不会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为受到伊恩的推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将要成为Ptolemaeus的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 能收到回应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪来的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是找我的…谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敌方基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向舰队传送可视加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 该去舰桥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点紧张吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧 稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 补给情况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0032结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向托勒密乘员以外全体人员传达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在0032出航
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业员在补给完成之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将本基地废弃 各种数据删除之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请乘运输艇 通过Y45路线脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在0037时 开始执行破坏联邦卫星兵器任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心点啊 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在托勒密?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己也有些能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用战斗也能做到的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去第2格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从三个方向 朝本基地的导弹攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的战力多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法解析
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌舰逃出同时 转入任务计划SA77
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点向第3格纳库移动!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输艇按顺序进发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请动作快!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位 请坐在那边的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机 发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 托勒密号的操作拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能专心炮击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止补给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密紧急发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把敌人引到我们身上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明… 明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给作业中止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密固定用机械臂解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机 已发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  0 Raiser的状况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再花些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚 将运输艇护卫到安全领域为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios 进入防御行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场 展开的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闸门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各连接机械臂切断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaeus 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰 出现!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4架Gundam也出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转入任务计划SA77
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军部队出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总数12架的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮蔽了热源…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 去迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预测的一样哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军部队 接近!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:14:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWINBUSTER-CANNON 高浓度压缩粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然作这种奇袭… 玛奈金!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军部队来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都别想!
